# Event Management System

Full-stack event management application with Node.js, Express, and MongoDB Atlas.

## Features

- ðŸ‘¤ User Registration & Management
- ðŸ“… Event Management
- ðŸ‘¨â€ðŸ’¼ Admin Dashboard
- â˜ï¸ MongoDB Atlas Cloud Database

## Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript
- **Backend:** Node.js, Express.js
- **Database:** MongoDB Atlas
- **Deployment:** DigitalOcean

## Installation

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/Diya2612/7th-assignment-copy.git
cd 7th-assignment-copy

# Install dependencies
cd server
npm install

# Create .env file
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your MongoDB URI

# Start server
npm start
```

## Environment Variables

- `PORT` - Server port (default: 3000)
- `NODE_ENV` - Environment (development/production)
- `MONGODB_URI` - MongoDB Atlas connection string
- `JWT_SECRET` - JWT secret key
- `SESSION_SECRET` - Session secret key

